<br>
If you are 46+ (I recommend being at least half way through 46th) and interested in attending please go to the GoB website and signup.<br>
<br>
Two groups will be going up, one at 7pm to do &quot;break&quot;, and one at 9pm with reinforcements. The raid will officially last until 1am EDT.<br>
<br>
For general information, loot tables, bestiary etc see...<br>
<!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/zones/Planes/Hate.htm">everquest.allakhazam.com/...s/Hate.htm</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
Class-specific armor for the following classes drop...<br>
 ...Mage, ShadowKnight, Cleric, Rogue, Warrior, Bard, Enchanter, Shaman.<br>
<br>
There are 2nd floor drops for Rangers, Druids and Paladins... BUT we have no plans on moving to the second floor on this raid, so likely no drops.<br>
<br>
The 'chest' mobs can drop, random chance, ANY planes armor so even if you don't have armor that drops in Hate you could get some anyways (and it would suck to let it rot, last raid a shaman and bard armor rotted). Also, if you do not receive anything during the raid you get to /random into a position for gems. Last raid we had over 30 gems to give out so everyone who attended got something, either armor or gem (I believe).<br>
